  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>Hardened against the extreme conditions found beneath the waves, this diving suit component is the perfect choice for both deep-water exploration and an afternoon's fishing.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一件专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>能够有效抵御海浪之下的极端环境，这件潜水服构件是探索深海或者是享受午后垂钓的绝佳选择。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>這款潛水衣元件能夠抵禦海面下的極端條件，是兼顧深水探險和下午釣魚的完美選擇。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
